<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>St. John's University may award advanced placement and college credit to those entering freshmen who earn a requisite score on the College Entrance Examination Board's Advanced Placement and/or CLEP Exams.  Placement, as well as the number of college credits appropriate to the academic development of the qualified student, is determined by the dean's office.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.stjohns.edu/academics/centers/dass/ufc/prospective/ap.stj" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

